{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"15bff54929","title":"给周世钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3a7ef3efd6","index":0,"year":1956,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"15bff54929"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"1d9487971c","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周世钊，又名东园，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学。当时任湖南省教育厅副厅长兼湖南省第一师范学校校长。"},{"id":"85a0aaa527","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"蒋竹如，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学。"},{"id":"8a48f7487e","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"曹子谷，即曹籽谷，解放前担任过湖南省教育厅厅长、湖南大学校长。新中国成立后，曾任湖南省政协常委、湖南省文史研究馆副馆长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d40323873c","type":"title","text":"给周世知的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929"},{"id":"1d9487971c","type":"paragraph","text":"东园兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929"},{"id":"85a0aaa527","type":"paragraph","text":"信及诗收读，甚快。我尚好。某先生楚辞，甚想一读。请你代候蒋竹如兄。又请你代候曹子谷以先生，谢谢他赠诗及赠南岳志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929"},{"id":"8a48f7487e","type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝平安","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929"},{"id":"ec3e08311b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929"},{"id":"c06c457850","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月廿九日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929"}],"page":{"id":"d1e9f8c815","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"15bff54929","start":204,"end":204}}}},"__N_SSG":true}